{"tid":939173,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"男子的手被動物園老虎咬住不放　他超淡定：跟我鬧著玩的啦","createTime":"2018-12-13T01:41:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-13T02:08:24.000Z","uid":141060,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"423e82fa139f01ffb89ac8e194a29dffdeb3e34b","tid":939173,"uid":141060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T01:41:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://lam777.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/962c7bb44fc2d911d2ade010ece68813-1-696x381.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Flam777.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F10%2F962c7bb44fc2d911d2ade010ece68813-1-696x381.png&h=0a6ec204&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n男子的手被動物園老虎咬住不放　他超淡定：跟我鬧著玩的啦<br />\n每次去參觀動物園，在獅子或老虎的牢籠外總是會貼滿警告標示說千萬不要接近牠們，被這些肉食性動物咬傷的話應該會超級慘烈的，不過竟然有一名男子不信邪，把手伸到關老虎的籠子裡，他不是太白目就是頭腦燒壞了吧&hellip;<br />\n▼這名男子一把手伸到籠內，老虎就張開血盆大口&hellip;<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.omgtw.com/upload/article/original/962c7bb44fc2d911d2ade010ece68813.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.omgtw.com%2Fupload%2Farticle%2Foriginal%2F962c7bb44fc2d911d2ade010ece68813.png&h=c572714f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▼直接看到底發生了什麼事！<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/21ZEIbjY9VI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F21ZEIbjY9VI&d=hc3C8GZ198Ygz40kVha4nbIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=6a966b8e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/21ZEIbjY9VI</a><br />\n呼&hellip;真的是讓人虛驚一場，看起來老虎並沒有要攻擊他的意思，好像還在跟他玩呢！<br />\n這到底是怎麼回事啊？原來這頭老虎是這個男的飼養的啦！他也有警告大家千萬不要隨便找一隻老虎這樣玩！他跟這隻老虎感情超級要好，才敢這樣做，他還會放任牠躺在床上跟自己撒嬌呢！<br />\n▼老虎躺在床上玩，旁邊的狗狗都看呆了，之後牠還跟主人討摸摸跟親親！<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Znpnf9D2VIk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FZnpnf9D2VIk&d=hc3C8GZ198Ygz40kVha4nbIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=cd3c71c2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Znpnf9D2VIk</a><br />\n天啊！難以想像老虎會像一隻小貓咪一樣做這些事，影片中的牠還真是越看越可愛了，主人也非常愛護牠呢！幸好最後都沒有發生什麼恐怖的事。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"140a01cd805235ff3511e54e31377acf0dcc06cd","tid":939173,"uid":33429,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T02:08:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/zQLtZrA.gifv\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FzQLtZrA.gifv&d=hc3C8GZ198Ygz40kVha4nbIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=710a0f2b\" target=\"_blank\">https://i.imgur.com/zQLtZrA.gifv</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/yyQI9PD.gifv\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FyyQI9PD.gifv&d=hc3C8GZ198Ygz40kVha4nbIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=04184ce8\" target=\"_blank\">https://i.imgur.com/yyQI9PD.gifv</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/KQdM9T7.gifv\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FKQdM9T7.gifv&d=hc3C8GZ198Ygz40kVha4nbIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=535d3934\" target=\"_blank\">https://i.imgur.com/KQdM9T7.gifv</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgur.com/SM5QtHy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2FSM5QtHy.jpg&h=7245c293&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}